{{Politics of Côte d'Ivoire}}
'''Communist Youth of Côte d'Ivoire''' (''Jeunesse Communiste de Côte d'Ivoire'') is a political youth movement in [[Côte d'Ivoire]]. JCOCI is the youth wing of the [[Revolutionary Communist Party of Côte d'Ivoire]].

On June 24, 2004, the General Secretary of JCOCI, Habib Dodo, was murdered by [[Student Federation of Côte d'Ivoire]] activists.<ref>[http://hrw.org/backgrounder/africa/cote1205/3.htm#_ftnref42 Human Rights Violations by Government Security Forces: 2005 Trends]</ref><ref>[https://www.humanite.fr/journal/2004-07-02/2004-07-02-396480. L'Humanite:  Balises, 2004-07-02]</ref>

