By a January 2014 estimation, the local community numbered 311 inhabitants in 64 homes.<ref>{{citation|url=http://www.nsinfo.co.rs/en/ds0503p |title=Broj stanovnika po mesnim zajednicama |publisher=JP Informatika Novi Sad |language=Serbian}}</ref>
