'''Toko'yoto''' or "Crab" was the [[Chukchi people|Chukchi]] god of the sea.<ref>{{cite book|title=Acta Universitatis Stockholmiensis: Stockholm studies in comparative religion|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ooXXp0UNeAwC|year=1961|publisher=Almqvist & Wiksell.|page=68}}</ref> Specifically, he was the creator and ruler of the [[Pacific Ocean]]. Some tribes refer to him as '''''Anky-Kele''''' and attribute to him the power over life and death.{{citation needed|date=September 2015}}

